# Solution: csharp_data_warehouse_expert_012_architectural_understanding_expert_01

## Key Files Identified

### Stream Processing Pipeline Modules
- /app/project/src/module_2.txt - TransformationLambda: Core Kinesis-triggered Lambda for real-time stream processing
- /app/project/src/module_72.txt - KinesisStreamProcessor: Stream processing entry-point with DI container, validates envelopes, selects transformation strategies
- /app/project/src/module_87.txt - KinesisTransformationFunction: Kinesis Lambda entry-point with strategy factory pattern
- /app/project/src/module_47.txt - Lambda handler for Kinesis with JSON source-generator for cold-start optimization
- /app/project/src/module_22.txt - Lambda with lazy ServiceProvider initialization for stream processing

### Batch Processing Pipeline Modules
- /app/project/src/module_10.txt - KpiTransformationEngine: Batch transformation engine with parallelism control, DeploymentLeadTimeStrategy with Timer-based flush
- /app/project/src/module_34.txt - KpiComputationEngine & Registry: Batch-oriented KPI computation with RawEventBuffer
- /app/project/src/module_53.txt - TransformationEngine: Core engine used by both Lambda handlers and Glue batch jobs
- /app/project/src/module_36.txt - FocusTimeRatioStrategy with StrategyExecutor for partitioned parallel batch execution
- /app/project/src/module_65.txt - EventTransformationPipeline using System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow for throughput optimization

### Transformation Strategy Modules (Shared)
- /app/project/src/module_7.txt - Transformation strategy registry with cold-start optimization
- /app/project/src/module_79.txt - TransformationStrategyRegistry: Singleton with reflection-based discovery, hot-reload support
- /app/project/src/module_8.txt - StrategyRegistry with lazy initialization and Lambda cold-start caching
- /app/project/src/module_38.txt - TransformationStrategyRegistry with assembly-based discovery

### Infrastructure/Configuration
- /app/project/src/config.txt - WarehouseOptions: Configuration with BatchWindowSeconds (60-3600 seconds), ParallelShardCount
- /app/project/src/constants.txt - PulseOpsConstants: Environment variables, resource names, metric definitions

---

## Code Evidence

### 1. Batch Processing High Startup Cost - Strategy Registry Discovery

```csharp
// File: /app/project/src/module_79.txt
// Lines: 143-184
private void DiscoverAndRegisterStrategies()
{
    var sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();

    IEnumerable<ITransformationStrategy> strategies = AppDomain.CurrentDomain
        .GetAssemblies()
        .SelectMany(asm =>
        {
            try
            {
                return asm.DefinedTypes;
            }
            catch (ReflectionTypeLoadException ex)
            {
                // Log and continue – some assemblies may fail to load.
                Console.Error.WriteLine($"[WARN] ReflectionTypeLoadException for {asm.FullName}: {ex.Message}");
                return ex.Types.Where(t => t != null).Cast<TypeInfo>();
            }
        })
        .Where(ti => ti is { IsClass: true, IsAbstract: false })
        .Where(ti => typeof(ITransformationStrategy).IsAssignableFrom(ti))
        .Select(ti =>
        {
            try
            {
                return (ITransformationStrategy)Activator.CreateInstance(ti)!;
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                Console.Error.WriteLine($"[ERROR] Failed to instantiate strategy {ti.FullName}: {ex}");
                return null;
            }
        })
        .Where(instance => instance != null)!;

    foreach (var strat in strategies)
    {
        RegisterStrategy(strat);
    }

    Console.WriteLine($"[INFO] TransformationStrategyRegistry discovered {_byStream.Count} strategies in {sw.ElapsedMilliseconds} ms.");
}
```

### 2. Batch Processing Timer-Based Buffering Strategy

```csharp
// File: /app/project/src/module_10.txt
// Lines: 282-366
internal sealed class DeploymentLeadTimeStrategy : IKpiCalculationStrategy, IDisposable
{
    private const string CommitEventType     = "CodeCommitPushed";
    private const string ProdDeployEventType = "CdPipelineDeployed";

    private readonly TimeSpan                               FlushInterval     = TimeSpan.FromMinutes(5);
    private readonly ConcurrentDictionary<string, DateTime> _commitTimestamps = new(StringComparer.Ordinal);
    private readonly Timer                                  _flushTimer;
    private readonly ILogger                                _logger;

    public string KpiName => "deployment_lead_time";

    public DeploymentLeadTimeStrategy(ILogger<DeploymentLeadTimeStrategy> logger)
    {
        _logger      = logger;
        _flushTimer  = new Timer(_ => FlushExpired(), null, FlushInterval, FlushInterval);
    }
    // ...
    private void FlushExpired()
    {
        var threshold = DateTime.UtcNow.AddHours(-24); // assume deploy happens within 24 h
        foreach (var kvp in _commitTimestamps)
        {
            if (kvp.Value < threshold && _commitTimestamps.TryRemove(kvp.Key, out _))
            {
                _logger.LogDebug(
                    "Dropped stale commit {CommitSha} for deployment lead-time KPI (older than 24h).",
                    kvp.Key);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

### 3. Configuration Showing Batch Window Limitations

