# Solution: csharp_data_warehouse_expert_012_architectural_understanding_expert_01

## Key Files Identified

### Stream Processing Pipeline Modules
- /app/project/src/module_2.txt - TransformationLambda: Core Kinesis-triggered Lambda for real-time stream processing
- /app/project/src/module_72.txt - KinesisStreamProcessor: Stream processing entry-point with DI container, validates envelopes, selects transformation strategies
- /app/project/src/module_87.txt - KinesisTransformationFunction: Kinesis Lambda entry-point with strategy factory pattern
- /app/project/src/module_47.txt - Lambda handler for Kinesis with JSON source-generator for cold-start optimization
- /app/project/src/module_22.txt - Lambda with lazy ServiceProvider initialization for stream processing

### Batch Processing Pipeline Modules
- /app/project/src/module_10.txt - KpiTransformationEngine: Batch transformation engine with parallelism control, DeploymentLeadTimeStrategy with Timer-based flush
- /app/project/src/module_34.txt - KpiComputationEngine & Registry: Batch-oriented KPI computation with RawEventBuffer
- /app/project/src/module_53.txt - TransformationEngine: Core engine used by both Lambda handlers and Glue batch jobs
- /app/project/src/module_36.txt - FocusTimeRatioStrategy with StrategyExecutor for partitioned parallel batch execution
- /app/project/src/module_65.txt - EventTransformationPipeline using System.Threading.Tasks.Dataflow for throughput optimization

### Transformation Strategy Modules (Shared)
- /app/project/src/module_7.txt - Transformation strategy registry with cold-start optimization
- /app/project/src/module_79.txt - TransformationStrategyRegistry: Singleton with reflection-based discovery, hot-reload support
- /app/project/src/module_8.txt - StrategyRegistry with lazy initialization and Lambda cold-start caching
- /app/project/src/module_38.txt - TransformationStrategyRegistry with assembly-based discovery

### Infrastructure/Configuration
- /app/project/src/config.txt - WarehouseOptions: Configuration with BatchWindowSeconds (60-3600 seconds), ParallelShardCount
- /app/project/src/constants.txt - PulseOpsConstants: Environment variables, resource names, metric definitions

